            <text>Atomic mass is usually an ____ mass of isotopes.</text>
            <option id="A">Average</option><option id="B">Exact</option><option id="C">Sum</option><option id="D">None</option>
            <answer>A</answer><explanation>Based on natural abundance.</explanation>
        </question>
